  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Reinforcement of border management capacities through the construction of the mobile border company HQ in Birnin Konni</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project seeks to create a Mobile Border Control Company within the Niger National Police as a means to strengthen Niger&apos;s border surveillance and management capacities. This intervention is intended to contribute to the development of border management capacities by providing operational teams with police barracks in the Tahoua region which in turn is expected to increase capacities to manage cross border flows, promote cross border cooperation and enhance surveillance capacities. To implement the proposed intervention, IOM will work closely with the Government of Niger as well as with EUCAP Sahel Niger.</narrative>
  </description>
